<plot>Documents the life-changing work done by the Plasticos foundation. Plasticos provides reconstructive surgery training in third-world countries for children and adults suffering from deformities and disfigurement. Lovely Rabbit tells the story of the beautiful people of Luangprabang, Laos and how Plasticos has reshaped their lives.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?345879</url></doc>
